ᱥᱤᱠᱷᱟ ᱫᱚ, [[ᱡᱮᱱᱤ ᱛᱷᱚᱢᱯᱥᱚᱱ]] ᱟᱨ [[ᱤᱱᱜ ᱰᱮ ᱵᱨᱩᱡᱤᱱ]] ᱫᱚ ᱟ.ᱰᱤ ᱜᱮ ᱯᱟᱝᱡᱟ(follow) ᱞᱮᱫ ᱠᱤᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ <ref>{{cite web|first=Purba | last=Dutt |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-12-22/people/28248947_1_women-swimmers-asian-games-athlete |title=Shikha Tandon, a pool of talent - The Times of India |publisher=The Times of India |date=2010-09-29 |accessdate=2010-10-11}}</ref>

